| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5508 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1caa32f1-a089-593f-9e7a-5951e3c5799c"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
